### Registrar novo usuário
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "admin123",
  "email": "admin@universidade.com"
}

###

### Login - Obter Token
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "admin123"
}

###

### Listar todos os alunos (SEM autenticação)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/alunos

###

### Listar todos os alunos (COM autenticação)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/alunos
Authorization: Bearer SEU_TOKEN_AQUI

###

### Buscar aluno por ID
GET http://localhost:5000/api/alunos/1
Authorization: Bearer SEU_TOKEN_AQUI

###

### Adicionar novo aluno
POST http://localhost:5000/api/alunos
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer SEU_TOKEN_AQUI

{
  "nomeCompleto": "João Silva",
  "dataNascimento": "2000-01-15",
  "cpf": "12345678901",
  "endereco": "Rua Teste, 123",
  "telefone": "11999999999",
  "email": "joao@email.com",
  "dataMatricula": "2025-01-15"
}

###

### Atualizar aluno
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/alunos/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer SEU_TOKEN_AQUI

{
  "id": 1,
  "nomeCompleto": "João Silva Santos",
  "dataNascimento": "2000-01-15",
  "cpf": "12345678901",
  "endereco": "Rua Nova, 456",
  "telefone": "11988888888",
  "email": "joao.santos@email.com",
  "dataMatricula": "2025-01-15"
}

###

### Deletar aluno
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/alunos/1
Authorization: Bearer SEU_TOKEN_AQUI

